# Report

## EXISTING STRUCTURES
Currently, there are no structures built on the map. The logs indicate that the agent attempted to place entities such as Wooden Chests and Transport Belts, but none were successfully placed due to various errors.

## ERROR TIPS

### Errors when placing entities on non-buildable tiles
- Ensure the tile is buildable before attempting to place an entity. Check the terrain and ensure no restrictions are present.

### Errors when placing entities on occupied tiles
- Verify that the target tile is unoccupied before placing an entity. Attempting to place a Wooden Chest or Transport Belt on an occupied tile will result in failure.

### General placement errors
- When encountering placement errors, review the environment and ensure that all conditions for placement are met, such as proximity to other entities and terrain suitability.

These tips should help in mitigating the errors encountered during the placement of entities and assist in successfully building structures on the map.
